  {
    "key": "combat|i_I_said_shut_up_i_screams_Ehstraffe_She_signals_at_the_t|40456eb0c210",
    "original": "<i>“I said shut up!”</i> screams Ehstraffe. She signals at the two soldiers guarding the pit, and they quickly hurry over to the stage. <i>“He is a silly man!”</i> she says, addressing the uncertain, murmuring mass of gold in front of her. <i>“He grows over-excited! He will get you all killed if you listen to him!”</i>",
    "translation": "",
    "stage": 0,
    "context": "&lt;&lt;POS:00359846&gt;&gt;"
  },
  {
    "key": "combat|i_Remember_the_last_riots_i_entreats_Ehstraffe_i_There|2578e21162ae",
    "original": "<i>“Remember the last riots!”</i> entreats Ehstraffe. <i>“There is only suffering when you pointlessly fight us! When you behave, when you are peaceful, there are nice things, are there not?”</i>",
